video.title: Criminal Minds: Suspect Behavior
video.synopsis: This spinoff series shifts to another team of elite FBI profilers in a unit tasked with learning to think like the cunning criminals they're tracking.

episodes.synopsis: While investigating the abduction of an 8-year-old white girl, Beth meets a distraught African-American woman who also is searching for her daughter.
episodes.title: Two of a Kind

episodes.synopsis: The team is called to Cincinnati, where three men were found dead in their hotel rooms. The suspect seems to lure her victims with sex.
episodes.title: Lonely Hearts

episodes.synopsis: The team arrives in Tucson, Ariz., to investigate the murder of a man whose body was found in his car with his eyes removed.
episodes.title: See No Evil

episodes.synopsis: Three people are killed from what the authorities believe to be serial sniper. The team canvasses the crime scene unaware they are being watched.
episodes.title: One Shot Kill

episodes.synopsis: A pipe bomb explodes at a Virginia high school. Cooper believes the bomber isn't finished when the team discovers a note at the scene.
episodes.title: Here Is the Fire

episodes.synopsis: A serial killer is killing random men by hanging. The crime scenes indicate there may have been someone with the unsub at the time of the murders.
episodes.title: Devotion

episodes.synopsis: When a Good Samaritan is killed while trying to stop an abduction of a young female, the team tries to track down the identity of the missing woman.
episodes.title: Jane

episodes.synopsis: An unsub is on a killing spree, demonstrating some deep-seated rage that won't stop until he's either killed or takes his own life.
episodes.title: Nighthawk

episodes.synopsis: Two young mothers are found brutally stabbed and their breasts violently mutilated -- yet their clothes were laundered and their hair and makeup done.
episodes.title: Smother

episodes.synopsis: A woman on death row for killing her mother and then influencing three teenage boys to kill their parents has inspired a rash of copycat crimes.
episodes.title: The Time Is Now

episodes.synopsis: When the daughter of a prominent judge is abducted, the team's investigation leads to a sexual sadist who may be working with an accomplice.
episodes.title: Strays

episodes.synopsis: People have shown up dead at camp sites with their faces mutilated. Evidence reveals that the perp may be attempting to remove skin from his victims.
episodes.title: The Girl in the Blue Mask

episodes.synopsis: An anonymous caller is forcing individuals to kill at random and in public by holding their loved ones hostage.
episodes.title: Death by a Thousand Cuts
